{"word":"Tyre","slug":"tyre","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tyre</b> 1. Kingdom of:<br/> - Hiram, king of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=1'>1Ki 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=3'>2Ch 2:3</a> <br/> - Hiram sends material to David for his palace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=3'>2Ch 2:3</a> <br/> - Men and materials sent from, to Solomon, for the erection of the temple and his castles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=11'>1Ki 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=11'>1Ki 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=16'>2Ch 2:16</a><br/><a href='S:Hiram'>Hiram</a> <br/> 2. City of Tyre, situated on the shore of the Mediterranean:<br/> - On the northern boundary of Asher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=29'>Jos 19:29</a> <br/> - Pleasant site of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=9&verse=13'>Hos 9:13</a> <br/> - Fortified<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=29'>Jos 19:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=7'>2Sa 24:7</a> <br/> - Commerce of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=28'>1Ki 9:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=11'>1Ki 10:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=23'>Isa 23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27'>Eze 27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=28&verse=19'>Eze 28:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=2'>Zec 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=3'>Act 21:3</a> <br/> - Merchants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=23&verse=8'>Isa 23:8</a> <br/> - Antiquity of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=23&verse=7'>Isa 23:7</a> <br/> - Riches of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=23&verse=8'>Isa 23:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=3'>Zec 9:3</a> <br/> - Besieged by Nebuchadnezzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=7'>Eze 26:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=29&verse=18'>Eze 29:18</a> <br/> - Jesus goes to the coasts of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=21'>Mat 15:21</a> <br/> - Jesus heals the daughter of the Syro-Phenician woman near<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=28'>Mat 15:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=31'>Mar 7:31</a> <br/> - Multitudes from, come to hear Jesus, and to be healed of their diseases<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=8'>Mar 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=17'>Luk 6:17</a> <br/> - Herod's hostility toward<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=23'>Act 12:23</a> <br/> - Paul visits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=7'>Act 21:7</a> <br/> - To be judged according to its opportunity and privileges<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=22'>Mat 11:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=14'>Luk 10:14</a> <br/> - Prophecies relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=45&verse=12'>Psa 45:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=87&verse=4'>Psa 87:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=23'>Isa 23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=25&verse=22'>Jer 25:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=27&verse=11'>Jer 27:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=47&verse=4'>Jer 47:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26'>Eze 26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=8'>Joe 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=10'>Amo 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=4'>Zec 9:4</a> "}]}